.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
City: new-york, edinburgh, venice, liverpool, london
Sport: lacrosse, climbing, cricket, ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. Nationality:british == Color:red
2. Nationality:swedish == Sport:cricket
3. Nationality:danish == Beverage:tea
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Beverage:coffee
6. City:venice == Sport:climbing
7. Color:yellow == City:edinburgh
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. City:london is on the left or right of Sport:lacrosse
11. Sport:skateboardings is on the left or right of City:edinburgh
12. City:new-york == Beverage:beer
13. Nationality:german == City:liverpool
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. City:london is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
